<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Featly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Featly,</orth> neatly, adroitly: <cit><quote>with sleided silk feat and affectedly enswathed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lc 48" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 48</bibl></cit> (the termination <emph>ly</emph> belonging to both adverbs). <cit><quote>foot it f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.380" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 380</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>she dances f.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.176" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 176</bibl></cit>.
